:"2021-01-25T19:55:02.000Z","msg":"Zain 啲片好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日串鳩啲支那仔同保皇黨"},{"pid":"9c6cd7613eeacddfb2403213d66b074f38cefee1","tid":2380214,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:52:09.000Z","msg":"南亞人好過叫阿叉"},{"pid":"181801883c42effbf863a9ff59840152f713b856","tid":2380214,"uid":189235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:44:01.000Z","msg":"原來個差係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98943fd5e035db0393efc2ce5b738c0fe91741fd","tid":2380214,"uid":52605,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:03:43.000Z","msg":"我都係從七丶八十年代港產片同啲老一輩人口中知道 阿差 呢個詞語 <br />\n有一段時間興過 印巴籍 呢個詞語 <br />\n但係原來佢哋都唔鍾意，跟住就變咗南亞裔"},{"pid":"dcc519c6ebb9e97b29e76b688d9a145a8c6c6cf1","tid":2380214,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94881b78a904531b748c0327739d9843dfe51e45","tid":2380214,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2d7ca3c3c8048a10d61d64ab8f8a2cffb5cad0b","tid":2380214,"uid":117237,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:05:13.000Z","msg":"用左蝻好多年<br />\n<br />\n好駛好用<br />\n又冇位比人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:08:49.000Z","msg":"好少真係叫人做阿差<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"叫個啲係死老嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68db22fede005fe448a6154da2fae83f2872fa8","tid":2380214,"uid":83328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"其實『阿星』、『Ali』呢類稱呼都可以接受，好似我個名就有『阿星』，或者你叫一聲『朋友』都好，但就唔好特登講歪啲，好似扮印度人講嘢咁，會覺得你笑緊我哋。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要屌就屌發哥啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JjAUTxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjAUTxB.png&h=bd122542&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4ade1ce381e68d94efd5ce93e5848a4fe6b13da","tid":2380214,"uid":50670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"Zain啲字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6493d39641e8cd207e737eccc9720ecdb905647b","tid":2380214,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"套電影佢自己鄉里拍，個片名係佢自己鄉里改用嚟自嘲，有咩就問返你同鄉啦"},{"pid":"e39bf06d274d3131db8c01089ed9507b384a76cb","tid":2380214,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T04:31:01.000Z","msg":"打從阿爺一代開始已在香港定居<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洋奴買辦後代 冇咩行差踏錯應該都發左"},{"pid":"9abe97ced4462f4accfa8d1528e87e7082ff6b0d","tid":2380214,"uid":387407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05e8817303ecf60a3b84ee92cc69445d9bbe1369","tid":2380214,"uid":34147,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T19:55:02.000Z","msg":"Zain 啲片好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日串鳩啲支那仔同保皇黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:42:50.000Z","msg":"最近果條冇字幕都好笑"},{"pid":"f2ca6dfcd88260ff10df92c460f73cb658d849ad","tid":2380214,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94881b78a904531b748c0327739d9843dfe51e45","tid":2380214,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2d7ca3c3c8048a10d61d64ab8f8a2cffb5cad0b","tid":2380214,"uid":117237,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:05:13.000Z","msg":"用左蝻好多年<br />\n<br />\n好駛好用<br />\n又冇位比人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:08:49.000Z","msg":"好少真係叫人做阿差<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:03:31.000Z","msg":"通常係上一輩d人叫慣左先會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}